{"TopicId":168317,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Engineers that can edit action groups would be cool.","CreatedByName":"Laz0rPhaz0r","CreatedById":183393,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-08T14:54:48Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Laz0rPhaz0r","CreatedById":183393,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-08T14:54:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello Squad,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni just thought that it might be cool if engineers with a certain lvl would be able to edit action groups during a mission. That would especially be useful for in-space-assembled ships. Or like Asteroid balancing if you could chose a specific engine to toggle on/off because stuff doesnt poit to the center of mass.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat do you think? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mrcarrot","CreatedById":176291,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-08T17:27:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCool idea! I like the sound of Bill EVAing to edit the action groups in Hard mode or using the capsule\u0027s computer in Easy. Have a rep!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-08T22:02:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3888852765\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/161919-131-en-es-de-action-group-manager-continued/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-09T14:10:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223238780\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022168317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221512770520\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed4738703795\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/161919-131-en-es-de-action-group-manager-continued/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would do the usual \u0022but they\u0027re taking about stock\u0022 reply, but as I don\u0027t think it\u0027s ever happening...yeah...there\u0027s a mod for that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cheif Operations Director","CreatedById":183218,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-09T14:19:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t mean to sound rude but we we go\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like the idea and definitely think it should be stock\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause believe it or not their is a CONSOLE COMMUNITY who would love this too and as much as we all want to download the fan to customize it that isn\u0027t going to happen so even though the vast majority of the community is on PC their are still many in this game for Console who want a playable game (which is coming) and also mods (which isn\u0027t coming) So instead of implements real solar system for everyone to be enabled (which should be done) a simple request like this is ridiculous to shoot down because of a existing mod. I\u0027m happy for the PC community and enjoy wanting modded videos for KSP, BUT it\u0027s annoying knowing the only way to get Modded KSP is to download a game (and buyPC) Given the fact it takes more than $100 for a game in my position I don\u0027t feel it is worth it and will continue to wait for Console Improved or what ever it is. I don\u0027t care if you shoot down something like real solar system like ideas with \u0022their a mod for that\u0022 but a simple idea like this can only improve the game for everyone. Real solar system isnt for everyone so not all would like it that being said this suggestion is for everyone it won\u0027t do any hard to community. Each engine would be togglebale via mission control or in craft is real life and so would almost every function so what\u0027s the problem. This would better KSP as a whole. Not just PC and theirs a mod for that\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-12-09T14:23:04Z\u0022 title=\u002212/09/2017 02:23  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 9, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Cheif Operations Director\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EMisspelled\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-09T16:15:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s amazing how much people will read into something and inject their own made up conversation to argue against.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll I did was post the mod link, I didn\u0027t\u00A0even type anything. Lol.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot sure where or how you inferred that I was \u0022shooting his idea down\u0022 but all I was doing was offering him a viable solution to his request that he could use right now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-09T18:46:54Z","Content":"\n\u003C